parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument cluster can cause the driver to lose visibility of essential vehicle information, such as speed and fuel level, which can lead to accidents or unsafe driving conditions.
symptoms: All instrument cluster lights are out
only warning and shift indicators are on
unable to see speed or fuel level.
